comment: dreamfit moratalaz is a big gym with lots of space and great stuff included like the sauna turkish bath and all group classes in one fee the cardio area has tons of machines so even when it s busy you ll usually find more free the instructors are amazing they are super motivating and full of energy my favourite classes so far are body pump latin dance cross and pilates but there are way more check the website haha they also have virtual classes which is a nice bonus i really like the gym overall it has everything i need just took off one star because it gets way too crowded especially the sauna and turkish bath i was excited for those but they re almost always packed crowded times 6 8 pm for the gym and honestly the sauna and turkish bath are full pretty much anytime i go i guess i ll have to start waking up early for the sauna also heads up if you want to pay a monthly sub make sure you have a spanish bank account otherwise you ll have to pay a full 31 day fee upfront
